主校區位於麥爾安得路，校區內包括人文和社會學系、科學和工程學系、王后大樓（Queens' Building）、人民宮（People's Palace）、主圖書館、學生會、一些研究中心及幾家餐館以及宿舍。<ref>{{cite web|title=Mile End, Queen Mary, University of London|url=http://www.qmul.ac.uk/about/howtofindus/mileend/index.html|accessdate=12 September 2011|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920120551/https://www.qmul.ac.uk/about/howtofindus/mileend/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="student guide 2011/12">{{cite web|title=Queen Mary, University of London Student Guide 2011–12|url=http://www.arcs.qmul.ac.uk/registry/student_guide_11-12.pdf|accessdate=12 September 2011|archive-date=2012-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402104027/http://www.arcs.qmul.ac.uk/registry/student_guide_11-12.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

